{"tid":2422208,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美領館壽臣山物業　恒隆宣布今日完成收購","createTime":"2021-02-25T04:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T04:55:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89b1cc1dbba930b997f11c2637c588fe53d3b354","tid":2422208,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EvC3f-tVgAAgLGI?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEvC3f-tVgAAgLGI%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3D900x900&h=594fabbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恒隆地產(00101)及恒隆集團(00010)聯合公布，完成向美國駐港總領事館收購香港壽山村道37號。<br />\n<br />\n該公司指出，香港特區土地註冊處獲告知美國已遵從該等外交義務，就該物業的出售獲得中國中央人民政府的書面同意，因此已為該協議備忘錄進行註冊。由投標人收購該物業的事項已於2021年2月25日完成。<br />\n<br />\n恒隆地產去年以25.66億港元購入壽臣山壽山村道37號物業，每平方呎作價54,138元。該物業於1983年落成，位處壽臣山，現為六幢低密度住宅物業，提供26個單位及52個車位，另設室外游泳池，物業採以交吉形式出售，不設「售後租回」條款，地盤面積約94,796平方呎，可重建面積約47,397平方呎。"},{"pid":"01b1c417bdf17877ca2b00ccbce0ff4c19cb0698","tid":2422208,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"美國低市價咁多賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ab14ec842f803989d60f4c2de5c55d9eec1857","tid":2422208,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"恆隆買樓都要問中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d03c8269f27596488548ac8e1b93c7ee56aed30","tid":2422208,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90ab14ec842f803989d60f4c2de5c55d9eec1857","tid":2422208,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"恆隆買樓都要問中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"個主席係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e1dabedeca